{"type": "article", "id": 16665, "title": "为什么你越来越爱用那些看起来丑而贱的表情？ | 好奇心研究所", "description": "事到如今，那些天真纯善的小熊小狗表情早已被淘汰，表情一定要“贱贱的”才能表达汹涌的感情。这用力过猛的世界！", "date": "2015-10-27T17:12:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}, {"id": 125, "name": "List"}], "genre": 1, "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 101671, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 222, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702111440mJQcUXnN4CaLfjWi.jpg", "contents": "\n<p>\n<span style=\"text-align:start;\">好奇心研究所的微博（</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982/home?from=page_100606&amp;mod=TAB#place\" target=\"_blank\">@好奇心研究所</a><span style=\"text-align:start;\">）和微信公众号（ID：</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">QLab42</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">）全面上线啦，微信<span>直接搜索「好奇心研究所」就可以订阅，</span>关注与所长亲密接触，赶紧的。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t为什么我爱用贱贱的表情：\r\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t1.  那就是我此刻真实的表情（@周韶宏）\r\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>2.  我就贱贱的啊（@5123）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.748\" height=\"374\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111434ysKz9rFhOZPjBbV7.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"500\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>3.  平时又不敢贱（@Rita）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>4.  而聊天的时候，文字表达自己恶俗的一面，真的好无力！（@Co 老師）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037\" height=\"463\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111435t6MjH0EVIThfkZ9z.jpg-w600\" title=\" \" width=\"1080\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>5.  轻度自轻自贱，双方就都可以更轻松（@基本无害）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>6.  还会让聊天气氛瞬间变好? （@wangwang）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.538\" height=\"269\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160726143950rAcshl7SKjp8i39Q.gif-w600Gif\" style=\"text-align:center;\" title=\" \" width=\"500\"/></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>7.  而且，你打不到我（@沐如风兮）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>8.  噫怪我咯？我这么多表情包（@有文化的高冷帅蠢驴?）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.69703872\" height=\"306\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111435EvZxowuApWd0hVK4.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"439\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>9.  笑着发出去就会吸引更多新表情诞生（@罗芊）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>10.  让我更自由地发挥喷薄而出的才（nao）华(dong)（@罗芊）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.56022409\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/201607021114364Dns120LYxr3fw9X.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"357\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t但有时候，贱贱的表情也是种掩饰：\r\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>11.  因为人贱人爱（@ones多太）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.418\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/2016070211143740o7pynQHCjWAg9R.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"500\"/><span> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>12.  而，自己平时又不可爱（@小豪从我游）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t13.  为了掩饰自己内心的不安（@浅眠者）\r\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>14.  为了让你爱上我……硬把自己拗成很有趣的样子！（@我诅咒不吃我面包的人）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" height=\"540\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/2016070211143748QlWqXr506cEAGw.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"540\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>15.  把对话气氛搞得 high 一点，虽然是假 high（@袁崟枫）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>16.  也好过，因为不能发表情而见面没得聊（@BraveMerida_）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.72296015\" height=\"381\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111438d5RI6ioGx9NKClcu.jpg-w600\" title=\" \" width=\"527\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>17.  总之，为了凸显我淫荡的内心，和直面人生的勇气（@yz） </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>18.  为了打入地球内部（@敷衍）</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>19.  为了爱与和平（@陈二） </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" height=\"500\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111438T4WHkM8t7exgGu3a.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"500\"/><span> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t20.  请收下这份动图包，深藏功与名（ @SmartP） \r\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\" \" class=\"\" data-format=\"gif\" data-ratio=\"0.43\" height=\"215\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702111439zmWipUMKVZHP2cJg.gif-w600Gif\" title=\" \" width=\"500\"/><span> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t以上条目均来自「好奇心研究所」我说栏目与微信公众号征集，你可以<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/mobs/519.html\" target=\"_blank\">在这里继续参与讨论</a>，也可以关注研究所微信公众号（搜索「QLab42」 或「好奇心研究所」），参与每周一的互动话题，下期答案看你的。\r\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n"}